{"tid":1238702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜突然咁多post叫林鄭連任？","createTime":"2019-06-18T02:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:06:57.000Z","uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02c1c14a8155a10e82eda994aec40bbc34b9b8e0","tid":1238702,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"叫林鄭下台<br />\n係要表現出香港抗爭對香港政府有控制權<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係中央話曬事</strong></span><br />\n中央企到幾硬係一回事 林鄭之後點死頂3年係一回事<br />\n但依個要求一定要有<br />\n先可以表達出今次香港人已對本屆政府完全不信任<br />\n再推一步就係執政危機<br />\n<br />\n你同我講無左林鄭就無仇恨值？<br />\n咁理應兩年前換左689就唔會有今日啦<br />\n結果咪一樣<br />\n重點不在人 而在體制<br />\n我地要一邊爭取林鄭下台，再一爭取普選<br />\n奪回香港既民主政制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭下台<br />\n重啟真普選政改</span>"},{"pid":"e7c97679f475041daac60eb7cc7302c0fd62c9d2","tid":1238702,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aeb5e0dcf1bbc719cf8edfebf23905596d2db10","tid":1238702,"uid":261530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1ca88338a5cba06fb6d48e547dca39b42b0b246","tid":1238702,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8aeb5e0dcf1bbc719cf8edfebf23905596d2db10","tid":1238702,"uid":261530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"Thanos可以團隊隊長同iron man<br />\n但thanos始終係thanos<br />\n你唔推倒佢 重啟政改<br />\n所有都會無限loop connect完都只係圍爐"},{"pid":"f79bfb4292421fbbffbe9e6f5c44613a653ce80d","tid":1238702,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc904049e315f8dab3f3fd06bfb24ea0354a9bf6","tid":1238702,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aeb5e0dcf1bbc719